question: Bạn hãy liệt kê mười món đồ có giá vốn nhập hàng thấp nhất nhưng lại mang về lợi nhuận dương cao nhất trên hệ thống bán lẻ Web
ground_truth_sql:
SELECT i.i_item_desc, ws.ws_net_profit
FROM web_sales ws
JOIN item i ON ws.ws_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
WHERE ws.ws_net_profit > 0
ORDER BY i.i_wholesale_cost ASC, ws.ws_net_profit DESC
LIMIT 10;
predicted_sql:
SELECT sub.i_item_desc,
       sub.i_current_price
FROM (
    SELECT i.i_item_desc,
           i.i_current_price,
           AVG(ws.ws_wholesale_cost) AS avg_cost,
           SUM(CAST(ws.ws_net_profit AS DECIMAL(18,2))) AS total_profit
    FROM web_sales ws
    JOIN item i ON ws.ws_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
    GROUP BY i.i_item_desc,
             i.i_current_price
    HAVING SUM(CAST(ws.ws_net_profit AS DECIMAL(18,2))) > 0
) sub
ORDER BY sub.avg_cost ASC,
         sub.total_profit DESC
LIMIT 10

question: Truy vấn tỷ lệ đơn hàng Clothing có khuyến mãi
ground_truth_sql:
SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN ss.ss_promo_sk IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLOAT) / COUNT(*)
FROM store_sales ss
JOIN item i ON ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
WHERE i.i_category = 'Clothing';
predicted_sql:
SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN ss.ss_promo_sk IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLOAT) / COUNT(*) AS promo_rate
FROM store_sales ss
JOIN item i ON ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
WHERE i.i_category = 'Clothing'
